quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  41,1,"Haa, miim."
  41,2,"Ko jipporiinde immorde ka Jurmetee…óo, Hinnotoo…óo on."
  41,3,"Deftere fensitaande aayeeje mum, janngeteende e …óemngal aarabu, wonan,de yim…ìe anndoo…ìe."
  41,4,"wewlinaynde jeertinaa…ìe. Kono …ìur…ìe …óuu…óude …ìen e ma…ì…ìe, …óuurnii, …ìeen …ìe nanataa."
  41,5,"∆Åe mb'i: "∆Åer…óe amen no ommbanii ko noddataa men e mum kon, noto hino e noppi amen, heedo kadi hino hakkunde amen e maa. Haray wonu e golle maa ; menen kadi mi…óen e golle amen"."
  41,6,"Maaku: "nganndee ko ne…ó…óanke yeruujo mon. Wahayinaama e am, won'de Dewetee…óo mon on, ko Dewetee…óo gooto. √ëii…ìee e …óum, insinano…óon mo". Bone woodanii sirkoo…ìe …ìen."
  41,7,"…ìe njonnataa …ìeen askal, hara kadi hi…ìe njeddi fii La'akara."
  41,8,"Pellet, …ìeen goo≈ã…óiin…ìe …ìe ngolli mo∆¥∆¥i …óin, hino woodani …ìe njo…ìdi ndi ta∆¥ondirtaa."
  41,9,"Maaku: "Eey mon on njedda oon tak…óo leydi ndin ndeer bal…óe …ói…ói, mba…óanon mo goree…ìe? Awa ko oon woni Jey…óo winndere ndeen."
  41,10,"O wa…ói pelle e dow mayri, O hebbini barki e mayri, O e…ì…ìi nguureeji mayri …óin e ndeer bal…óe nayi timmu…óe, wonan'de lamndotoo…ìe …ìeen."
  41,11,"Refti o fotondiri ka kammu, fewndo ka ngu curkinnoo, O daalidani ngun kanngu e leydi ndin: "ngrdiree …óoftaare, maa karheede". ∆äi wi'idi: "Min ngarii ko min …óoftii …ìe"."